  "notes": "Rabies Category III post-exposure prophylaxis (group 'b' sheets Qtr1b-Qtr4b). Two completion metrics with DIFFERENT denominators: ARV+RIG completion is measured against patients WITHOUT prior ARV history (need full PEP + immunoglobulin); ARV-only completion against patients WITH prior history (boosters only). Both denominators are within this sheet. Linked Category-III exposure columns (idx 3-5) are cross-sheet references to base and NOT re-ingested. Reconciliation DQC (no-history + with-history == Cat III total; ARV+RIG + ARV-only <= Cat III total) deferred to the D4 rule type."
